The <strong><code>ondurationchange</code></strong> property of the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers" title="The GlobalEventHandlers mixin describes the event handlers common to several interfaces like HTMLElement, Document, or Window."><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> mixin is the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventHandler" title="REDIRECT DOM event handlers"><code>EventHandler</code></a> for processing <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/durationchange" title="/en-US/docs/Web/Events/durationchange">durationchange</a></code> events.